Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:32.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:40.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:02:04.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:11.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:27.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:35.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:52.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:32.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}爬上這一帶視野最美的那棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:40.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}孩子笑了 笑得天真無邪 她看到了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:02:04.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}定定地盯著空中暢游的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:11.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小鎮每個角落裡漸漸褪色的日子浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}拉鉤上吊百年不變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}即使分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:27.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}等待約定實現的心情也寄託在這顆樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一遍一遍地重複
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:35.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每次都止不住淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}停下來又繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}彷彿是要印證這一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:52.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}山間回音響不絕 你說是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========ED================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:26.26,ED,,0,0,0,,夜の水面に飛び交う蛍が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.12,ED,,0,0,0,,流れ星みたいできれーなのん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.77,ED,,0,0,0,,どこからともない雉鳩の声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.57,ED,,0,0,0,,モノマネしながらいく でこぼこ道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.99,ED,,0,0,0,,澄み渡る星空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.97,ED,,0,0,0,,いつのまにか並んで眠ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,朝日がおかえりって微笑んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:08.50,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しい おかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.21,ED,,0,0,0,,さりげない日常 ふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,抱きしめてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一暖かい 春が訪れる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:38.43,ED,,0,0,0,,ほら 花のこえが聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:26.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}夜晚的水面上飛來飛去的螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就像是流星一般好美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知何處傳來了雉鳩的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}踏著凹凸不平的小路 邊走邊玩模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我們在繁星遍佈的澄空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知不覺就並排著睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}朝陽微笑著歡迎我們回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:08.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我們回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那些平平淡淡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}輕輕地擁抱我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最溫暖的地方 是春天到訪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:38.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}豎起耳朵來 能聽到花兒的聲音喔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 早上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 麵包吃完了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 今天姐姐就親手下廚做料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在春天的蔬菜上淋上沙拉油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒點椒鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 可以吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:03:01.03,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(503,576)}在\N連\N休\N中\N鼓\N起\N幹\N勁\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始就是黃金週了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可還要考試真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…雖然我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如果當旁觀者的話就很有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待著不動就會睏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從後面開始收上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收卷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我打完分很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這等下一場考試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩考得不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不怎麼樣 國語我不是很擅長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海考得…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這太沮喪了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國語要掛… 國語要掛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考得那麼差嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我答不出來 是題目太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『請寫出作者這時候的感覺』那種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是那個作者 鬼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他邊想『好想吃咖哩』邊寫也有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說這些有什麼用…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最有可能的不是『截稿日快到了怎麼辦』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好煩人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 這種心煩的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太鬱悶了 姐姐也這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的卷子裡面又沒有這種題目…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,┐(￣3￣)┌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏的感覺是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不明白是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大概就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國語就是┐(￣3￣)┌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垂頭喪氣也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海的考試現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種台詞更叫人不安了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一場考試是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是理科吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理科我已經放棄了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英語有點… 我是日本人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就考完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海的考試就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 果斷放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出題比做題爽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 螢 說十次『Pizza』試試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza Pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是膝蓋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}ひざ(hiza)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連出題都出錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄去學習呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非哥哥對英語有自信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我英語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我生氣了 所以把眼鏡搶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息時間都快完了你還在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 理科我已經放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出一下英語的題目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想自己複習呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 你想想 如果我的分數太爛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的怒火可能也會燒到姐姐身上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 麻煩畫一下後面可能會出的題目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 把這篇文章翻譯成日語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中學生夠嗆呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從上下文看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鮑伯說 『這是大象嗎？』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『不 是河童』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗噗 錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後不是河童 是螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是鮑伯錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鮑伯錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 蓮醬和螢也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒有說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大象和螞蟻 不可能搞錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家問題上就那麼寫的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不來了 果然還是放棄英語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理科拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 休息時間只剩下五分鐘了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙子葉植物的根部是由什麼組成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一直不動 很冷淡的樣子 不過本性很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}註：雙關，ね = 根部 / 性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：主根與側根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你看他們開花把花蜜送給昆蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本性很溫柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 都是我剛剛想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個就不要管了 快點出下一題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,細菌繁殖方式是把細胞一分為二 這種現象被稱為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色森巴舞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：細胞分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯微鏡這個部分的名稱是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉輪彈倉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}註：左輪手槍裝子彈的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：物鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒有機物會釋放什麼氣體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼煙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聞氨的氣味時應該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乞求饒命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：用手把氣味扇出來聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子這個部分的名稱是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是把牙刷塞鼻子裡面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：嗅球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種生物的名稱是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹中家的爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}答案：水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 能成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼能這麼自信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後那個真的合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在氣勢如虹了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點開始考試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有幹勁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不寫名字就是零分 要注意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海搞得定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海搞得定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海搞得定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏海搞得定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能成 小夏海Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成 能成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 這是剛才做過的題目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是笹中家的爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這題剛才也做過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這題也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 小夏海可能是個天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼把今天的試卷發回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果分數有問題的話就拿過來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比估計的還要差呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡 有點問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有寫名字還是零分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為全部答錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,┐(￣3￣)┌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始是黃金週
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過整體來說都不夠理想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在要佈置作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做旁觀者太有趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佈置了好多作業呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為夏海得了零分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐放開我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是看到這種地方居然有螳螂 想把它抓住而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螳螂？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到姐姐你衝過來的時候真是嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為你拿了零分要發洩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會覺得我會發洩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來我家做作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏和螢 小小鞠和哥哥也過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 是兩點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到時候見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 小小鞠他們會來我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠他們會來我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家來一起學習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 為了學習佈置了很多作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 知道電視遙控器在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 幫我拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我覺得那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在為拿到好成績努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是老師在考試期間卻一副想睡覺的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家也一直睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連拿個遙控器都不去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣連小夏都會學了你 一直沒有幹勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得老師的工作是讓大家提起幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說讓我鼓起大家的幹勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輔導大家學習可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 還要靈活運用胡蘿蔔和大棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話在大家來到之前做鼓起幹勁的練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼短時間就能成功的話就沒那麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 我做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我裝作在學習的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想姐姐以老師的身份鼓起我的幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 扮家家酒的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這絕對不是扮家家酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是正式的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 蓮醬 在學習嗎 好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫我寫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在學國語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 名字後面的『わ』是寫成『は』喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在學算術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是算術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等號的前後都是數字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要試試把學習當成遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,題目是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬是勇者打倒它們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒之後更強的敵人就會出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好有趣的樣子 我有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 第一題是史萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用鉛劍幹掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉛劍… 是說鉛筆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 史萊姆打倒了 蓮醬升級了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 下一個敵人 下一個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 下一個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叮隆叮隆叮隆叮隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火橘子出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 不知火橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 那不就是個大橘子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這道題可能會讓你嚐到辛酸的味道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,432)}不知火橘子看著這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是不知火橘子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且接下來的第三題是不及格陷阱·博多草莓先生喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不過第四題是蜜瓜王子所以可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然如果來的是夕張的話就沒勝算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}註：夕張產的蜜瓜被稱為『蜜瓜大王（夕張キングメロン）』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 第五題是火龍果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可會噴火喔 糟了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和魔物戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是出來的怎麼都是水果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 老實說我沒怎麼玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了史萊姆以外就想不到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼姐姐還說要玩遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些遊戲裡還會有什麼其他東西出現的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 裝備上鉛劍的話連龍都可以幹掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不削尖了裝備上的話就沒意義了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起和水果戰鬥 我還是想吃掉它們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答出那條題的話 就獎勵蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐 姐姐 什麼時候買蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水果蛋糕嗎 巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以 我剛好想吃蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 沒有買喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是說一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得能提起你的幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 蓮醬能不能幹掉不知火橘子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火橘子是兩位數減法 會不會太難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扮家家酒已經玩夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心已經做完減法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 蓮醬 幹勁減太多了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 教育方法就不說了 從精神面貌上改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果老師值得信賴的話 就能鼓起幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要駝背
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有去學校的時候穿制服應該會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘子 橘子答出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天姐姐比平常還要貪睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我叫過你要打起精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我昨天晚上做講義做到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本沒怎麼睡過覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夜晚工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是昨天我沒見到你工作呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在蓮醬睡覺之後深夜才做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒搞清楚還把姐姐叫醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過蓮醬都那麼說了 姐姐也要加油了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐現在就睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把體力保存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習有什麼地方不懂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就隨時把我叫起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不過 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 蓮醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著看我教大家學習 鼓起大家的幹勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這睡覺的話 會打擾到人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在這個房間學習呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果姐姐完全沒有幹勁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是去被窩裡睡好點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 把我帶到被窩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼呢 那點事一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶我嘛 脫眼罩太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連脫眼罩都嫌麻煩 只是摘下來一下而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然姐姐已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來鼓起大家的幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始要打起精神來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 拖鞋在那 穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想姐姐就那樣轉一下圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那樣的話就不認識方向了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常做的話就不好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 就像打西瓜那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著往那邊一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有階梯 小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 走廊裡面有階梯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續一直往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的休息日 為什麼要學習呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如回家閒著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續閒著成績又下降的話 又要被媽媽罵了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你看一直沒有幹勁的穗姐都活得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不用好好努力也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前一片黑 找不到枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『一片黑』 『枕頭』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,200,0,,{\fs32}まっくら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.77,*Default,NTP,250,0,0,,{\fs32}まくら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 戳到笑點了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮 蓮醬 蓮醬 聽見了嗎聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『一片黑』和『枕頭』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}蓮醬 剛剛聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}『一片黑』和『枕頭』
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 蓮醬好像變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 枕頭在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七十五分呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起學習見效了 補考拿到好成績了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呀 努力了就有回報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得和之前說的完全不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又拿到一百分啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這紅豆麵包的餡 只放了咖哩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 所以說 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是肉碎咖哩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒放豆餡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這甜味和辣味的組合 是非常重要的
Comment: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,Trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青蛙是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌蚪是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後腿出來花錢養
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前腿出來叛逆期
